response.overview: Fifteen original shot-on-film theatrical XXX trailers from the year 1973. Includes Flying Acquaintances, The Big Switch (Things Change), The Birds and The Beads, The Bride’s Initiation, Come and Be Purified, Come Deadly, Devil in Miss Jones, Fly Me!, Frankie and Johnnie Were Lovers, Girls in the Penthouse, Grace’s Place, Rise, Hitler’s Harlot, Hot Channels, and Hungry Eyed Woman.
response.title: Cumming Attractions 1973 Vol. I
